'''過氧化物酶體增殖物活化受體''' 或稱為 '''脂小體增生活化受體'''（Peroxisome proliferator-activated receptor，PPARs）在[[分子生物學|分子生物學]]的領域裡，是一組[[核受體|核受體]][[蛋白|蛋白]] ，具有[[轉錄因子|轉錄因子]]的功能，以調控[[基因|基因]]表達<ref name="Michalik_2006">{{cite journal | author = Michalik L, Auwerx J, Berger JP, Chatterjee VK, Glass CK, Gonzalez FJ, Grimaldi PA, Kadowaki T, Lazar MA, O'Rahilly S, Palmer CN, Plutzky J, Reddy JK, Spiegelman BM, Staels B, Wahli W | title = International Union of Pharmacology. LXI. Peroxisome proliferator-activated receptors | journal = Pharmacol. Rev. | volume = 58 | issue = 4 | pages = 726–41 | year = 2006 | pmid = 17132851 | doi = 10.1124/pr.58.4.5 }}</ref>。這組核受體蛋白對高等生物的[[細胞分化|細胞分化]]、[[發育生物學|發育]]與[[新陳代謝|新陳代謝]]（{{le|碳水化合物代謝|Carbohydrate metabolism|碳水化合物}}、{{le|脂質代謝|Lipid metabolism|脂質}}、{{le|蛋白質代謝|Protein metabolism|蛋白質}}）及[[癌变|癌变]]的發生有着關鍵的作用<ref name="pmid19609453">{{cite journal | author = Belfiore A, Genua M, Malaguarnera R | title = PPAR-gamma Agonists and Their Effects on IGF-I Receptor Signaling: Implications for Cancer | journal = PPAR Res | volume = 2009 | issue = | pages = 830501 | year = 2009 | pmid = 19609453 | doi = 10.1155/2009/830501 | url = | issn = | pmc = 2709717 }}</ref><ref name="Berger_2002">{{cite journal | author = Berger J, Moller DE | title = The mechanisms of action of PPARs | journal = Annu. Rev. Med. | volume = 53 | issue = | pages = 409–35 | year = 2002 | pmid = 11818483 | doi = 10.1146/annurev.med.53.082901.104018 }}</ref><ref name="Feige_2006">{{cite journal | author = Feige JN, Gelman L, Michalik L, Desvergne B, Wahli W | title = From molecular action to physiological outputs: peroxisome proliferator-activated receptors are nuclear receptors at the crossroads of key cellular functions | journal = Prog. Lipid Res. | volume = 45 | issue = 2 | pages = 120–59 | year = 2006 | pmid = 16476485 | doi = 10.1016/j.plipres.2005.12.002 }}</ref>，能夠控制环境与饮食刺激。其中受体α主要参与[[肝细胞|肝细胞]]的氧化过程。受体δ则参与了[[脂肪细胞|脂肪细胞]]的分解过程，受体γ与脂肪细胞的生成过程有关，这两个受体被认为与肥胖有关。本类受体只有與{{le|视黄醇类X受体|Retinoid X receptor}}（RXR）结合后才会发生作用<ref>{{cite journal| language =zh| author =邹颖，王勇，吴效科| title =过氧化物酶体增殖物活化受体与胰岛素抵抗| url =http://www.lw23.com/pdf_8278a6cc-7ba6-40ae-981c-0c78bec5e2a0/lunwen.pdf| journal =中国公共卫生| volume =23| issue =3| pages =371-372| year =2007| id =1001.0580(2007)03—0371.02}}{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。{{protein
